### Update exercise - replace id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Incline Bench Press"
}

### Update exercise - multiple fields
PATCH http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Low Bar Squat",
  "description": "Low bar back squat",
  "category": "LEGS"
}

### Update exercise - nonexistent id
PATCH http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc-id-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost Exercise"
}

### Update exercise - empty body
PATCH http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Delete exercise - replace id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc

### Delete exercise - nonexistent id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/fd5ec71c-ffa4-486f-a29b-89d8e2b5a7bc-id-123

